<html>
<header>
  <%- include ('../../partials/header.ejs') %>
  <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/main.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/konva@4.0.0/konva.min.js"></script> -->
</header>

<body>
  <div id="achievement" style="display: none;">
    <h1></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="app">
    <div class="header">
      <h1 id="title">Bobby's Breakout</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="main">
      <div id="info" class="info">
        <div id="premium_content" style="display: none;">
          <h2>You're premium!</h2>
          <h3>Benefits:</h3>
          <ul id="premium_benefits">
            <li>Exp + 10%</li>
            <li>Loot drop RNG + 10%</li>
            <li>And more...</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div id="instructions">
          <h2>Instructions</h2>
          <p>Escape Simon Fraser University as THE Bobby Chan, famous lecturer trying to get home to his wife.</p>
          <p>Either fight your way out, or escape silently. The choice is yours.</p>
          <p>You're the grey block. Go to the red exit to complete each level. NPCs are the yellow blocks and they can
            see in a square in front of them.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="controls">
          <h2>Controls</h2>
          <ul class="controls">
            <li><img src="assets/icon_wasd.png"> Move</li>
            <li>
              <div class="key">E</div>
              Interact
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="key">P</div>
              Pause
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="key">I</div>
              Open/Close Inventory
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="key">Y</div>
              Add a test item to the inventory
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="key">X</div>
              Add a test achievement to achievements
            </li>
          </ul>
          <form class="form" action="/login">
            <button type="submit" id="logoutbtn">Logout</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="container" class="game">
      </div>
      <div id="inventoryMenu" class="menu">
          <div>
            <button id="dropButton">Destroy</button>
            <button id="equipButton">Equip</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="equippedMenu" class="menu">
          <div>
            <button id="unequipButton">Unequip</button>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <script type="module" src='scripts/main.js'></script>
</body>

</html>
